nodes.text: Star Wars: X-Wing Deluxe Book and Model Set

Star Wars: X-Wing Deluxe Book and Model Set is an X-wing model kit published by Insight Editions as part of their IncrediBuilds collection. The kit includes a laser-cut, FSC-certified wood sheet, step-by-step instructions, coloring and crafting ideas, and an X-wing guidebook, titled Inside the Galaxy's Most Versatile Starfighter, written by Michael Kogge. It was released on October 18, 2016.
